section.para:
@sts@ runs on Eclipse using Java Version 1.6, and @webserv@ requires Java Version 1.6. 
The @greenpages@ application built here also requires Java Version 1.6.
You should not need to alter the default Java compiler settings in @sts.short@ before proceeding.

@maven.full@, or @maven@ for short, is a software project management and comprehension tool
which uses a central Project Object Model (POM) to manage a project’s build, reporting 
and documentation generation. POM files (pom.xml) are included in the projects for
@greenpages@.
